        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Services Section -->
  <section id="services" class="py-16 md:py-24 px-4 md:px-6 bg-gradient-to-b from-white to-slate-50">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
      <!-- Section Header -->
      <div class="text-center mb-12 md:mb-16">
        <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 mb-6">
          <div class="h-px w-8 md:w-12 bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-orange-400 to-transparent"></div>
          <span class="text-orange-400 font-bold text-xs md:text-sm uppercase tracking-widest">
            Social Media Services
          </span>
          <div class="h-px w-8 md:w-12 bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-orange-400 to-transparent"></div>
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-cyan-900 leading-tight mb-4 md:mb-6 px-4">
          Complete <span class="text-orange-400">Social Media Solutions</span>
        </h2>
        <p class="text-base md:text-lg text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4">
          From strategy to execution, we manage every aspect of your social media presence
          to build engagement, grow followers, and drive real business results.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Services Grid -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6 md:gap-8">
        {socialMediaServices.map((service) => (
          <CardService
            icon={service.icon}
            title={service.title}
            description={service.description}
            learnMoreUrl={service.learnMoreUrl}
          />
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Platforms Section -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-20 px-4 md:px-6 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-cyan-900 mb-4">
          We Master <span class="text-orange-400">Every Platform</span>
        </h2>
        <p class="text-base md:text-lg text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          From Facebook to TikTok, we understand each platform's unique algorithms and best practices.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-4 md:gap-6">
        {platforms.map((platform) => (
          <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-50 to-white border border-gray-200 rounded-2xl p-6 hover:shadow-xl hover:scale-105 transition-all duration-300 text-center group">
            <div class="text-4xl mb-3 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">
              {platform.icon}
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-sm md:text-base font-bold text-cyan-900">{platform.name}</h3>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- What is Social Media Marketing Section -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-24 px-4 md:px-6 bg-gradient-to-b from-slate-50 to-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8 md:gap-12">
        <!-- Main Content -->
        <div class="lg:col-span-2">
          <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 mb-6">
            <div class="h-px w-8 md:w-12 bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-orange-400 to-transparent"></div>
            <span class="text-orange-400 font-bold text-xs md:text-sm uppercase tracking-widest">
              Understanding Social Media
            </span>
            <div class="h-px w-8 md:w-12 bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-orange-400 to-transparent"></div>
          </div>

          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-cyan-900 mb-6 leading-tight">
            What is <span class="text-orange-400">Social Media Marketing?</span>
          </h2>

          <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none text-gray-600 leading-relaxed space-y-4">
            <p>
              Social media marketing is the strategic use of social platforms to connect with your audience, build brand awareness, drive website traffic, and increase sales. It involves creating and sharing content, engaging with followers, running paid advertising campaigns, and analyzing results to optimize performance.
            </p>

            <p>
              In today's digital landscape, social media has become essential for businesses of all sizes. With billions of active users across platforms like Facebook, Instagram, LinkedIn, TikTok, and Twitter, social media provides unparalleled opportunities to reach and engage your target audience where they already spend their time.
            </p>

            <p>
              Effective social media marketing goes beyond simply posting content. It requires a deep understanding of each platform's unique algorithms, audience behaviors, content formats, and best practices. A successful strategy combines creative content creation, community engagement, data analytics, and paid advertising to achieve measurable business results.
            </p>

            <p>
              The power of social media lies in its ability to create authentic, two-way conversations between brands and consumers. Unlike traditional advertising, social media enables real-time interaction, instant feedback, user-generated content, and viral sharing that can exponentially amplify your message and build genuine brand loyalty.
            </p>

            <p>
              From building brand awareness and generating leads to providing customer service and driving e-commerce sales, social media marketing has become an indispensable tool for modern businesses seeking to compete and thrive in the digital age.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Sidebar -->
        <div class="lg:col-span-1">
          <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-cyan-900 to-cyan-800 rounded-2xl md:rounded-3xl p-8 text-white sticky top-8">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6">Social Media Impact</h3>

            <div class="space-y-6">
              <div class="border-l-4 border-orange-400 pl-4">
                <div class="text-3xl font-black text-orange-400 mb-1">4.9B+</div>
                <div class="text-sm text-cyan-100">Global social media users in 2024</div>
              </div>

              <div class="border-l-4 border-orange-400 pl-4">
                <div class="text-3xl font-black text-orange-400 mb-1">151min</div>
                <div class="text-sm text-cyan-100">Average daily time spent on social media</div>
              </div>

              <div class="border-l-4 border-orange-400 pl-4">
                <div class="text-3xl font-black text-orange-400 mb-1">76%</div>
                <div class="text-sm text-cyan-100">Of consumers buy from brands they follow</div>
              </div>

              <div class="border-l-4 border-orange-400 pl-4">
                <div class="text-3xl font-black text-orange-400 mb-1">93%</div>
                <div class="text-sm text-cyan-100">Of marketers use social media for business</div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="mt-8 pt-6 border-t border-cyan-700">
              <p class="text-sm text-cyan-100 leading-relaxed">
                Social media marketing delivers an average ROI of $2.80 for every dollar spent, making it one of the most cost-effective marketing channels available.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Why Choose Us Section -->
  <Whyus />

  <!-- Benefits Section -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-20 px-4 md:px-6 bg-gradient-to-b from-slate-50 to-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-cyan-900 mb-4">
          Why Choose <span class="text-orange-400">Codebrand</span>
        </h2>
        <p class="text-base md:text-lg text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          Our social media approach combines creativity, analytics, and platform expertise for maximum impact.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 md:gap-8">
        {benefits.map((benefit) => (
          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl md:rounded-3xl p-8 shadow-lg hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-300 border border-gray-100">
            <div class="text-5xl mb-4">{benefit.icon}</div>
            <h3 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-cyan-900 mb-3">{benefit.title}</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">{benefit.description}</p>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-20 px-4 md:px-6 bg-gradient-to-br from-cyan-900 via-cyan-800 to-cyan-900">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-black text-white leading-tight mb-6">
        Ready to <span class="text-orange-400">Go Viral?</span>
      </h2>
      <p class="text-base md:text-xl text-cyan-100 mb-10 leading-relaxed px-4">
        Let's create a social media strategy that captures attention, builds community,
        and drives measurable results for your business. Start growing your presence today.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center items-center">
        <Button text="Start Growing Now" href="/contact" />
        <a href="/services" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-6 md:px-8 py-3 md:py-4 bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm text-white font-bold rounded-full hover:bg-white/20 transition-all duration-300 border border-white/30 text-sm md:text-base">
          <span>View All Services</span>
          <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 7l5 5m0 0l-5 5m5-5H6"></path>
          </svg>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FAQ Section -->
  <Faq />
</Layout>

<style>
  @keyframes fade-in {
    from {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(10px);
    }
    to {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translateY(0);
    }
  }

  .animate-fade-in {
    animation: fade-in 0.6s ease-out;
  }

  .delay-1000 {
    animation-delay: 1s;
  }
</style>
